of your bedroom last time?

00:24:22.719 --> 00:24:24.319
Yes.

00:24:24.319 --> 00:24:26.010
Yes?

00:24:26.680 --> 00:24:28.329
You Shu Lang.

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:32.079
Do you know who he is?

00:24:32.079 --> 00:24:34.160
He's Fan Xiao.

00:24:34.160 --> 00:24:35.280
The one who hired me as a model.

00:24:35.280 --> 00:24:36.719
