00:25:19.920 --> 00:25:21.640
But what are you doing here?

00:25:21.640 --> 00:25:24.370
Pervert, what do you want?

00:25:27.599 --> 00:25:28.800
I get it.

00:25:28.800 --> 00:25:32.400
Your ex is my current boyfriend.

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:33.903
Right?

00:25:37.119 --> 00:25:39.359
All because I once turned you down,

00:25:39.359 --> 00:25:42.560
and now I'm with the boyfriend you abandoned,

00:25:42.560 --> 00:25:47.089
so you snapped?

00:25:48.800 --> 00:25:50.079
It's not like that.

00:25:50.079 --> 00:25:51.770
That's not true.

00:25:52.560 --> 00:25:53.959
It's not like that, Uncle You.

00:25:53.959 --> 00:25:56.119
Don't listen to him.

00:25:56.119 --> 00:25:58.119
It's my fault. I was base.

00:25:58.119 --> 00:25:59.800
I shouldn't have left you for him.

00:25:59.800 --> 00:26:01.560
But he's a pervert.

00:26:01.560 --> 00:26:03.160
A master manipulator.

00:26:03.160 --> 00:26:04.520
I don't know why he played me

00:26:04.520 --> 00:26:06.199
and now came for you.

00:26:06.199 --> 00:26:08.239
There must be a connection.

00:26:08.239 --> 00:26:10.071
There must be.

00:26:15.239 --> 00:26:17.640
- There must be.
- Lu Zhen.

00:26:17.640 --> 00:26:19.650
Calm down.

00:26:27.040 --> 00:26:29.880
Speak slowly.

00:26:29.880 --> 00:26:31.530
Don't get worked up.

00:26:38.520 --> 00:26:41.160
Zhen Zhen, sit. Slow your breathing.

00:26:41.160 --> 00:26:43.520
Once you calm down,

00:26:43.520 --> 00:26:44.839
we can resolve our differences.

00:26:44.839 --> 00:26:47.130
Don't call me that!

00:26:47.880 --> 00:26:50.400
Lu Zhen, sit.

00:26:50.400 --> 00:26:52.040
Eat the chocolate.

00:26:52.040 --> 00:26:53.920
Your lips are pale.

00:26:53.920 --> 00:26:56.160
It's low blood sugar.

00:26:56.160 --> 00:26:58.280
Control your emotions.

00:26:58.280 --> 00:27:01.280
I don't want you fainting here,

00:27:01.280 --> 00:27:04.689
because I no longer have
any duty to care for you.

00:27:10.040 --> 00:27:11.479
Fan Xiao.

00:27:11.479 --> 00:27:13.040
Lu Zhen's anemic.

00:27:13.040 --> 00:27:15.640
He can't take verbal stress.

00:27:15.640 --> 00:27:17.119
If your taunts today

00:27:17.119 --> 00:27:19.680
make him pass out here,

00:27:19.680 --> 00:27:22.560
the responsibility
of looking after him falls on you.

00:27:22.560 --> 00:27:24.169
After all...

00:27:25.400 --> 00:27:28.530
he was your life model once.

00:27:33.760 --> 00:27:35.610
I'm going to change.

00:27:38.119 --> 00:27:41.169
You're wrapped up tight.
Why are you changing?

00:28:00.425 --> 00:28:02.876
Lust blinds judgment.

00:28:03.640 --> 00:28:07.010
It's all self-deception.

00:29:07.812 --> 00:29:09.623
Put your clothes on.

00:29:24.680 --> 00:29:26.199
I have several questions.

00:29:26.199 --> 00:29:28.399
You can choose not to answer.

00:29:28.399 --> 00:29:31.040
But if you won't,

00:29:31.040 --> 00:29:33.880
