00:29:40.119 --> 00:29:41.959
It's not appropriate.

00:29:41.959 --> 00:29:43.160
Lu Zhen.

00:29:43.160 --> 00:29:45.839
How did Fan Xiao find you as a model?

00:29:45.839 --> 00:29:47.479
Ms. Xiao Ya called me.

00:29:47.479 --> 00:29:48.839
I didn't want to go.

00:29:48.839 --> 00:29:51.479
I had other gigs.

00:29:51.479 --> 00:29:53.079
She told me to drop them

00:29:53.079 --> 00:29:54.319
because this one paid a lot.

00:29:54.319 --> 00:29:55.920
He asked for you by name?

00:29:55.920 --> 00:29:58.160
Yes, he specifically asked for me.

00:29:58.160 --> 00:30:00.760
Fan Xiao, did you give Lu Zhen gifts?

00:30:00.760 --> 00:30:02.400
I did.

00:30:02.400 --> 00:30:04.959
Just to thank him.

00:30:04.959 --> 00:30:06.959
Small things.

00:30:06.959 --> 00:30:08.319
Nothing expensive.

00:30:08.319 --> 00:30:11.400
The crown was from you too?

00:30:11.400 --> 00:30:13.319
I gave it.

00:30:13.319 --> 00:30:16.160
At their ad shoot,

00:30:16.160 --> 00:30:18.689
I happened to see him get bullied.

00:30:19.560 --> 00:30:21.280
We're friends.

00:30:21.280 --> 00:30:23.359
I couldn't just watch.

00:30:23.359 --> 00:30:24.920
You know how it is.

00:30:24.920 --> 00:30:26.880
Favors for favors.

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:29.959
I had the host send him the crown.

00:30:29.959 --> 00:30:33.239
That day, Lu Zhen came to pick up the painting.

00:30:33.239 --> 00:30:35.689
You heard his voice from the room.

00:30:36.640 --> 00:30:39.239
Didn't you recognize your friend was here?

00:30:39.239 --> 00:30:41.049
I didn't recognize his voice.

00:30:42.959 --> 00:30:44.610
Lu Zhen.

00:30:45.319 --> 00:30:47.599
The day you picked up the painting,

00:30:47.599 --> 00:30:49.809
